Packages that use it.apice.sapere.api.space.match
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.compilers This package contains entities capable of converting an Eco-law to SPAR(Q|U)L queries. 
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.scheduling This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaw ratings, involved in ecolaw scheduling logic. 
it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.scheduling.impl This package contains eco-law rating functions. 
it.apice.sapere.api.space.core This package contains LSA-space internals interfaces. 
it.apice.sapere.api.space.core.impl This package contains LSA-space internals interfaces implementation. 
it.apice.sapere.api.space.match This package contains it.apice.sapere.match entities tests. 
it.apice.sapere.api.space.match.impl This package contains eco-law matching facilities implementation. 
it.apice.sapere.management This package contains all the entities dedicated to eco-laws scheduling. 
it.apice.sapere.management.impl This package contains all the implementations dedicated to eco-laws scheduling. 
 

Classes in it.apice.sapere.api.space.match used by it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.compilers
